						<label>M16A2 IF</label>
						<canBeToggled>true</canBeToggled>
						<separateToggle>false</separateToggle>
					</li>
					<li>
						<label>Pulsefire</label>
						<canBeToggled>true</canBeToggled>
						<separateToggle>false</separateToggle>
						<description>The Pulsefire Under-Barrel Flamethrower (UBF) is a portable incendiary projector that was designed to be mounted to various different weapon platforms, being compatible with standard picatinny and similar rail mounting configurations. It does not require a separate fuel tank or battery source, with the system being completely self-contained.</description>
					</li>
				</verbProps>
			</li>
